  <brief_title>Study Comparing Olanzapine With Haloperidol for the Relief of Nausea and Vomiting in Patients With Advanced Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Double-blind, Parallel Group Study Comparing Olanzapine (Zyprexa) With Haloperidol (Novo-peridol) for the Relief of Nausea and Vomiting in Patients With Advanced Cancer</official_title>
